%H A396461 Sander G. Huisman, <a href="/A396461/a396461_2.png">Image of the first 10^7 grid positions.</a>
%H A396461 Sander G. Huisman, <a href="/A396461/a396461_3.png">Image of the first 10^8 grid positions.</a>
%e A396461 The grid is as follows:
%e A396461   0  1  8  9  24 25
%e A396461   3  2  7  10 23 26
%e A396461   4  5  6  11 22 27
%e A396461   15 14 13 12 21 .
%e A396461   16 17 18 19 20 .
%e A396461   .  .  .  .  .  .
%e A396461 And gets occupied as follows:
%e A396461   K A . A . K
%e A396461   K F K K . A
%e A396461   F K . A K .
%e A396461   A . F K . A
%e A396461   . F K F A K
%e A396461   . A . F . F
%e A396461 Where the . means that the position remains unoccupied.
